469e4e89-82f2-4f69-9424-d9836ba36f53	ff68e952-b7ee-4034-af62-07c9d79660f1	Law 2: Make It Attractive (Craving)	\N	<p>Habits are dopamine-driven feedback loops. The more attractive a habit is, the more likely it is to be adopted. Temptation Bundling is a strategy that pairs an action one wants to do with an action one needs to do. For example, only allowing oneself to listen to a favorite podcast while exercising. The enjoyment of the "want" becomes associated with the "need," making the habit more attractive. Joining a Supportive Culture is another technique. Humans are social creatures who desire to fit in. One of the most effective ways to build better habits is to join a culture where the desired behavior is the normal behavior. To get fit, join a gym or running club. To read more, join a book club.</p>	https://media.lilde.com/media/%40_The-Stable-Reset/MP3/022.mp3	\N	\N	22	OVERFLOW	0	0	2025-10-17 16:40:10.024858	2025-11-07 16:45:54.119642	light	0.00	0.00	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
